column3: “Nice strain, gives a head high and after some minutes you are veeery stoned. Watch out, likely to cause paranoia and psychosis.”
“That's very good indica, body stone + strong head trip, it helps to sleep very good and allows to concentrate without problems.”
“not a good taste but good feeling very strong stone high”
“A good high, not the best tasting.”

“At first i'm pretty clear headed for a few minutes. When it really hits, it makes me stoned for another 30 minutes, than I find everything pretty funny (even when I'm all alone) for an hour or more. Than it makes me hungry.
Smell is not that good, but not bad at all. 
Still a 5 for it's effect.”
“Super good strain easy to grow, first 3 hits will make you laugh and then you are gonna need a couch”
“Variedad expectacular, he probado muchísimas que prometen sobre 20%thc y esta lo cumple con creces. La mejor raza que he probado en mi puta vida!!!”
